snippet.title: GUNHEAD - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/704000/GUNHEAD/

Gunhead is a fast paced roguelike FPS where you take the role of a pirate mech with a gun for a head, looting derelict spaceships filled with monstrous drones made out of bone and steel. A sequel to Alientrap’s previous 2d game Cryptark
Coming 2018
